---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy | coolLabs">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-6xl px-4">
    Refund Policy<span class="text-warning">.</span>
  </h1>
  <h2 class="text-base pb-10 pt-2 text-neutral-400 px-4">
    Our commitment to your satisfaction.
  </h2>

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 pb-8">
    <div class="text-left text-neutral-400">
      <p class="mb-2">
        <strong class="text-warning">Effective Date</strong>: July 3, 2023
      </p>
      <p>
        At coolLabs Solutions Kft. ("we", "us", or "our"), we strive to ensure
        your satisfaction with our services. If you are not fully satisfied with
        your purchase, we offer a 30-day refund policy under the following
        terms:
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        Our products may include links to external sites not operated by us.
        Please be aware that we have no control over their content or privacy
        practices, and this policy does not apply to them.
      </p>

      <h3
        class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl pt-12 pb-4"
      >
        Eligibility<span class="text-warning">.</span>
      </h3>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Timeframe</strong>: Refund requests must
          be submitted within 30 calendar days from the date of purchase.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Services Covered</strong>: This policy
          applies to all paid Coollabs services, including subscriptions to
          Coolify, Fonts, or other hosted solutions.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Usage</strong>: Refunds are eligible for
          accounts without any usage limitation.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3
        class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl pt-12 pb-4"
      >
        Non-Eligible Cases<span class="text-warning">.</span>
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-4">Refunds will not be granted for:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
        <li class="mb-2">
          Violations of our Terms of Service (e.g., misuse of resources).
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">
          Requests submitted after the 30-day period.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h3
        class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl pt-12 pb-4"
      >
        Refund Process<span class="text-warning">.</span>
      </h3>
      <ol class="list-decimal ml-6">
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Submit a Request</strong>: Contact our
          support team at hi [(at]) coollabs.io with your account details and
          reason for the refund request.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Review</strong>: We will review your
          request within 5 business days to confirm eligibility.
        </li>
        <li class="mb-2">
          <strong class="text-warning">Processing</strong>: Approved refunds
          will be processed to the original payment method within 10 business
          days. Refunds will exclude any transaction fees charged by payment
          processors.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <h3
        class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-2xl pt-12 pb-4"
      >
        Contact Us<span class="text-warning">.</span>
      </h3>
      <p>Questions or want to request a refund? Reach out to us:</p>
      <ul class="list-none mt-2">
        <li>
          <strong class="text-warning">Email</strong>: hi [(at])
          coollabs.io
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="text-warning">More Info</strong>:
          <a
            href="https://coolify.io/docs/contact"
            class="text-warning hover:underline">https://coolify.io/docs/contact</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mt-4">
        coolLabs reserves the right to modify this refund policy at any time.
        Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
